---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div class="relative" id="home">
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 grid grid-cols-2 -space-x-52 opacity-40 dark:opacity-20">
        <div class="blur-[106px] h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-purple-400 dark:from-blue-700"></div>
        <div class="blur-[106px] h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-sky-300 dark:to-indigo-600"></div>
    </div>
    <Container>
        <div class="relative pt-36 ml-auto">
            <div class="lg:w-2/3 text-center mx-auto">
                <h1 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl xl:text-7xl">Empowering your business with <span class="text-primary dark:text-white">tailored industry solutions.</span></h1>
                <p class="mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Shuxuan is a data intelligence solution provider specializing in data analysis and aiding product efficiency through data-driven AI. We also help businesses innovate and enhance profitablity with scientific-based decision making.</p>
                <div class="mt-16 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-y-4 gap-x-6">
                    <a
                      href="mailto:myfinance888@gmail.com"
                      class="relative flex h-11 w-full items-center justify-center px-6 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-full before:bg-primary before:transition before:duration-300 hover:before:scale-105 active:duration-75 active:before:scale-95 sm:w-max"
                    >
                      <span class="relative text-base font-semibold text-white"
                        >Contact Us to Get Started</span
                      >
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden py-8 mt-16 border-y border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 sm:flex justify-between">
                    <div class="text-left">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Data Fusion / Integration</h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">The Shuxuan data fusion system stands apart from typical big data company data management platforms. It represents Shuxuan's unique big data product, achieved through the integration of diverse big data resources and the application of data analysis technology alongside intelligent labeling algorithms.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-left">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Data Analysis</h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">Shuxuan's well-established market research division is among the largest in the country, boasting abundant resources, methodologies, and knowledge bases. They excel in conducting comprehensive market research for entire business chains of enterprises and also cater to government research needs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-left">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Data Implementation</h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">Shuxuan's data application focuses on delving deep into the core of enterprise operations, offering more than just decision-making support. This encompasses fully data-driven CRM precision marketing, artificial intelligence technology deployment, government big data initiatives, smart city projects, intelligent tourism solutions, and ecological advancements, among others.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </Container>
</div>